column5: Pregame and Superbowl later???  Thanks in advance!
Not my Footsball League    National Felons League
CTV is carrying it. Lucky for me this time, no streaming required. I pick it up with rabbit ears just siting on my Samsung TV. Not even hooked up. The station is right across the road.
What is this footy ball you speak of?  It's not played on ice is it?  If so I may gain some interest...
